# Destination App Color Palette

The primary brand color revolves around a **Golden Amber** derived from the company logo, which stays consistent across both themes, while surfaces and typography adjust accordingly.

## ☀️ Light Mode Palette (Default)

| Color Category | Variable | Hex Code / Value | 
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Primary (Brand)** | `--primary` | `#F5B731` |
| | `--primary-hover` | `#E5A520` |
| | `--primary-light` | `#FEF3CD` |
| | `--primary-dark` | `#B8860B` |
| **Surfaces** | `--background` | `#F0F1F5` (App Background) |
| | `--surface` | `#FFFFFF` (Card/Container Background) |
| | `--surface-elevated` | `#F8F9FA` |
| | `--surface-hover` | `#F3F4F6` |
| **Typography** | `--text-primary` | `#1A1A2E` |
| | `--text-secondary` | `#6B7280` |
| | `--text-muted` | `#9CA3AF` |
| | `--text-on-primary`| `#1A1A2E` |
| **Borders** | `--border` | `#E5E7EB` |
| | `--border-focus` | `#F5B731` |
| **Sidebar** | `--sidebar-bg` | `#1A1A2E` (Dark Sidebar in Light Mode) |
| | `--sidebar-text` | `#CBD5E1` |

